sentences.en: All they do is make Yankees madder and put off the day when they could get back.

sentences.en: If they've got to buy black votes like the Yankees have done, then they will buy black votes.

sentences.en: If they've got to vote ten thousand dead men like the Yankees did, every corpse in every cemetery in Georgia will be at the polls.
